item.description:
allokkio  Thinking by Tinkering. A experiment blog where I collect short-notes, sketches and ideas.
Epper Eppes Still a fledgling. A (more ordered) complement to the craze of allokkio. Here I will collect lists, microsites, zines and similar things.
visCOS R. The package visCOS, the package cosCOS; and the idea of rrrCOS are my take for providing a unified way to guide the calibration of the rainfall-runoff model COSERO from &lsquo;R&rsquo;
